{"article_id":"t94GFCNsTTdl7XMv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"ObamaCare made it through nearly 10 months of repeal attempts with Republicans in full control of Washington .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"It ' s the first test","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"of how the Trump administration will handle enrollment under the law","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"it claims","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"is \" imploding. \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"With the president making no secret of his desire","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"to kill the law completely ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Democrats accuse the administration of `` sabotage ''","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and say","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"the number of new enrollees is likely to drop as a result .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"That would lift the uninsured rate ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"which has fallen dramatically","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"since the law went into effect ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and could hurt ObamaCare ' s sustainability","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"by leaving a smaller , sicker and costlier pool of enrollees .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" There ' s a renewed urgency","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that I haven ' t seen in the past couple of years , \"","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"said Lori Lodes , a former Obama administration health official","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"who runs Get America Covered , a group","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"working with local officials","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to fill the gap","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"left by the Trump administration ' s cuts .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Since Trump came into office ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"he has taken a series of actions","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that could undermine the law .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"He signed an executive order","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that instructed agencies to loosen ObamaCare rules ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"slashed advertising and outreach dollars ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"cut enrollment staff","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"and earlier this month cut off payments to insurers","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"that reimburse them","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"for giving discounts to low-income enrollees .","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"One influential analyst predicts","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"confusion from these actions will lead enrollment to drop several million","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"compared to last year .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Charles Gaba projects","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the numbers could drop to between 9.5 and 10 million people this year , down from 12.2 million last year ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"though he notes","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"it is hard to predict .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Josh Peck , a former Obama administration health official , has estimated","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that the new administration ' s cutbacks to outreach alone will lead to 1.1 million fewer people","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"signing up for coverage this year .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Gallup found this month","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"that the uninsured rate has already started to tick back up this year after a sharp decline","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"when ObamaCare went into effect in 2014 .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Since the law went into full effect ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"the number of uninsured has dropped from around 45 million to 28 million .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"The Trump administration will also not put out an enrollment goal this year , in a break with the practice under Obama .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"The administration faces a difficult balancing act","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"in overseeing a law","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"it opposes","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"but that is still on the books .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Department of Health and Human Services","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"( HHS )","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"officials pushed back on the idea","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"they are sabotaging the law ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"arguing","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that ObamaCare was already flawed .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"The administration says","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"it will still be carrying out many functions , like a call center and email alerts to consumers .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Asked if the administration wants the sign-up period to go smoothly ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"an HHS official said","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"\" absolutely . \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"However , the administration slashed funding for advertising and outreach by 90 percent","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"and cut funding to outside groups ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"known as navigators ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that help people enroll .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"More broadly , experts say","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"the several near-misses in Congress","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"to repeal the law this year","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"could leave consumers wondering","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"if ObamaCare is even still in effect .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"President Trump ' s recent comments","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that the law is \" dead \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"are not helping ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"according to Ceci Connolly , CEO of the Alliance of Community Health Plans .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"\" Some folks might hear that","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"and think","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"either ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"' I don ' t have to sign up for insurance anymore ,","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"'","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"or maybe ' my insurance isn ' t available , ' \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"said Connolly ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"whose group includes community-based health insurers ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"many of which participate in the ObamaCare markets .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Trump ' s decision","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"to cut off the payments to insurers","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"has also led to some premium spikes","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"as insurers try to compensate for the loss .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Connolly said","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that her insurer group had \" no heads up whatsoever \" before Trump 's move earlier this month .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"An official with America ' s Health Insurance Plans","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"( AHIP )","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"that she is \" hopeful \"","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"that the ObamaCare markets will continue to stabilize","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"but that uncertainty from the administration and Congress has been an obstacle .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"\" The uncertainty has certainly been challenging this year","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"and we 're hoping to get on some more level footing next year , \"","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"said Kelley Turek , AHIP 's executive director of employer and commercial policy .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"She added","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that insurers are \" trying to step up to the plate a little bit more \" in their outreach efforts to consumers","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"to fill the gap","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"left by the administration ' s cutbacks .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"The enrollment period is about half as long this year ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"ending Dec. 15 , another focus of messaging .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"The Trump administration pushed back on the idea","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"that its cuts are part of an effort","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"to sabotage the law .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"\" It ' s important to remember that ObamaCare enrollment was in decline","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"before President Trump took office , \"","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"said HHS spokesman Matt Lloyd .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Enrollment dropped from 12.7 million in 2016 to 12.2 million in 2017 ,","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"though Democrats argue","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"that Trump administration cutbacks in January played a role .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"\" The previous administration inflicted heavy damage on the individual market","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"- premiums doubled ,","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"insurers dropped out of the individual market in droves ,","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"millions of Americans saw their plans cancelled","depth":18},{"id":119,"text":"because Washington didn ' t approve of them ,","depth":18},{"id":120,"text":"and millions more paid billions in fines","depth":17},{"id":121,"text":"to avoid the kind of coverage","depth":17},{"id":122,"text":"ObamaCare dictated , \"","depth":17},{"id":123,"text":"he added .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"\" That ' s not evidence of a healthy , competitive market","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"nor one","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"that is best serving individuals and families . \"","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"If enrollment falls significantly short this year ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"it could hurt the stability of the law ,","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"given that the people","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"most likely to remain","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"are the sickest enrollees","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"who most need health insurance","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"and are the costliest .","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"\" If enrollment drops","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"and healthy people drop out","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"the effect would be destabilizing , \"","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"said Larry Levitt , a health policy expert at the Kaiser Family Foundation .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"\" In this political environment what happens during open enrollment will be really important both symbolically and practically . \"","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"But experts emphasize","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"that the law is still on the books","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"and financial assistance is still available","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"to help people afford coverage .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"\" We 're really trying to make sure","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"that consumers are aware of the fact","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"that things aren ' t really changing that much , \"","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"Turek said .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":151,"right":292,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":0,"right":150,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":1,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":2,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":292,"left":193,"right":291,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":193,"left":167,"right":192,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":160,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":155,"right":159,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":152,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":7,"right":153,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":159,"left":157,"right":158,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":10,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":161,"right":165,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":1